# Placeholder for presentation assets

This folder contains editable diagram sources and screenshots for the presentation.

## Folder Structure

```
assets/
├── .gitkeep (this file)
├── er_diagram.drawio (ER diagram - Chen notation)
├── er_to_relational.drawio (ER → Relational mapping)
├── normalization_before_after.drawio (Normalization example)
└── screenshots/ (captured during demo)
```

## Usage

- **drawio files:** Open in https://app.diagrams.net/ or desktop Draw.io app
- **screenshots:** Captured using SHOTLIST.md as guide

## Notes

- drawio XML files are text-based and Git-friendly
- Screenshots should be PNG format (1920x1080)
- Do NOT commit large binary files (> 5 MB)
